  **Compliance Frameworks**:
  - **None Explicitly Mentioned**: All exemplars operate in research contexts; no certification requirements noted.
  **Interoperability Standards**:
  - **Partial**: AutomationML (Air Quality) enables cross-platform digital twin integration.
